flowchart LR
    SELLER[Seller - verified RSU student] --> UI[Gravity web interface - mobile-first HTML/CSS/JS]
    BUYER[Buyer - verified RSU student] --> UI

    UI --> REG[Register / verify screen]
    UI --> FORM[Create Listing form + validation]
    FORM --> STORE[(JSON seed + localStorage)]
    STORE --> LIST[Listings page - search and category filter]
    LIST --> DETAIL[Listing detail view + verified badge]
    DETAIL --> REQ[Contact request - reveal after both agree]
    REQ --> STORE
    STORE --> DASH[Dashboard - totals by status and category]

    ADMIN[Admin - Gravity team] --> ADMINP[Admin panel]
    ADMINP --> VERIFY[Approve student verification]
    ADMINP --> STATUS[Update status / remove listing]
    VERIFY --> STORE
    STATUS --> STORE
